    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stitches made with a double purl, used to finish the edges of tailored buttonholes and to form a secure edge in cut work. For similar stitches are further apart used for thick fabrics use "blanket stitches." </Note_Text>
